                <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/2241: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">at Geneva</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-04-30T16:00:00-04:00"
                            >April 30, 1934—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>143. Your 236, April 26, noon. Our information from Bogotá, Lima and Rio de
                    Janeiro appears to warrant optimism as to the possibility of direct settlement
                    between Colombia and Perú in the present negotiations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
